<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-387-464  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 387 464.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  June 27 1989 v3 n25 p8(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT MacWEEK Inc. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Insight puts Mac on payroll. (accounting software) (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Adams, Eric J.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Layered Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   Insight Expert Accounts Payable (Accounting software) (productenhancement)Insight Expert Payroll (Accounting software) (productintroduction)Apple Macintosh (Microcomputer) (computer programs).andO;Topic:     AccountingSoftware PackagesModules.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Eric J. AdamsandM;Boston -- Layered Inc., which last month released atOnce!, an entry-levelaccounting program, has added another module to its high-end Insight ExpertAccounting package.andM;The $695 Payroll module, which completes the Insight series introduced in1987, can either stand alone or work with other Insight modules.andM;The program can handle an unlimited number of employees, a wide variety ofpay cycles, unlimited earning codes, and numerous deduction and taxationoptions.andP;  It can also  capture accounts from the Insight General Ledger,automatically print payroll checks and generate recurring payroll.andM;Insight's improved print manager supports a variety of report-formattingoptions.andP;  Among the reports the program can produce automatically is ExpertWage Analysis, which graphically displays pay amounts for the past 10 payperiods and forecasts cash projections for the coming five weeks.andP;  Like theother Insight modules, Payroll can import and export data from most databasesand spreadsheets.andM;Layered Inc. is located at 529 Main St., Boston, Mass.andP;  02129; (617)242-7700; (800) 622-4436.andO;</TEXT></DOC>